================
How to test code 
================

Install pytest with

pip install pytest
pip install pytest-cov

# test all
pytest

# test all in one file
pytest test_multiple_line_expresssions.py

# show output
pytest -s

# test only one function
pytest -v test_multiple_line_expresssions.py::test_change_indices_in_einsum3

# to get code coverage use (need to have pytest-cov installed)
pytest --cov

# ... more detail
pytest --cov --cov-report html --cov=myproject .

